{
  "stem": "9156.8",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 18.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Paul got, finally, the visa, too, and it is about a month after that I am in the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And his story is-- again, that should be separately told someday, because they go on a boat in Marseilles-- I will only say that quickly.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were a whole bunch of refugees, but they had no idea that a whole bunch of Nazis was on that boat, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that they, Nazis, had decided that when they come to-- and I forget now the name of the island-- that they will then get all these refugees and kill them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on the way, while they were on the high seas, a Dutch boat under English command bombs that boat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The German-- the Nazis throw everything that they have into the water because they where the enemies.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Dutch capture the boat, and there are all these refugees, and there are all these Nazis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the-- the Dutch-- no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The refugees said, this is terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How do we communicate?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But thank god that Paul knows this strange, low German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so he could explain who they are were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They get them to Trinidad, and they were supposed to. and they were interned in Trinidad.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they wanted to put them all into one internment camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Paul went with two others and said, if you do that, and tomorrow morning there are only cut throats.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We will not stay one night with these people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They either cut ours or we cut theirs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were fortunately separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Meanwhile, in New York, the embassy heard about all that, and I forgot the name of the American embassy at that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
